OL,3,CMountain rescue and emergency services
OL,4,Csave three capsized people
OL,6,FMountain rescue volunteers helped
OL,7,Femergency services save three people
OL,8,Fwho had capsized in a lake over the
OL,9,FBank Holiday weekend.
OL,11,FThe Keswick Mountain Rescue Team was
OL,12,Fcalled out to assist in what it
OL,13,Fdescribed as a "major multi-agency
OL,14,Foperation", after an inflatable canoe
OL,15,Fcapsized on Derwentwater on Saturday,
OL,16,FApril 4.
