OL,3,CMountain rescue and emergency services
OL,4,Csave three capsized people
OL,6,FBy Saturday morning - before the
OL,7,Fforecasted peak of Storm Dave -
OL,8,Fconditions on Derwentwater had become
OL,9,Frough and unsuitable for light leisure
OL,10,Fcraft.
OL,12,FThree individuals were involved in the
OL,13,Fincident, none of whom wore flotation
OL,14,Fdevices.
OL,16,FOne of the group had made it to shore,
OL,17,Fand another had reached St Herbert's
OL,18,FIsland, while a third remained in the
OL,19,Fwater.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
