OL,3,CMountain rescue and emergency services
OL,4,Csave three capsized people
OL,6,FAlongside the Keswick MRT, the
OL,7,FWhitehaven Coastguard Rescue Team,
OL,8,FMaryport Coastguard Rescue Team, and
OL,9,Fthe HM Coastguard Helicopter,
OL,10,Falongside Cumbria Police, Fire and
OL,11,FRescue, NWAS, and the Great North Air
OL,12,FAmbulance all took part in the rescue.
OL,14,FThe Keswick Launch and Derwent Water
OL,15,FMarina also helped the rescue crews
OL,16,Fnavigate the stormy conditions.
OL,18,FAll three of the individuals involved
OL,19,Fwere safely rescued, before being
OL,20,Fassessed by the air ambulance team as
OL,21,Frequiring no hospital treatment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
