OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775481061
OL,3,CMountain rescue and emergency services
OL,4,Csave three capsized people
OL,6,F16 responders were involved in saving
OL,7,Fthe occupants of the capsized craft,
OL,8,Fin a rescue which took 38 minutes.
OL,10,FThe Keswick Mountain Rescue Team said:
OL,11,F"This incident serves as a stark
OL,12,Freminder of how quickly conditions can
OL,13,Fturn.
OL,15,F"If you are heading out on the water,
OL,16,Fplease always wear a buoyancy aid - it
OL,17,Fbuys you vital time if you end up in
OL,18,Fthe water."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
